name: Les Colors du Sud Z&
description:
Collab Thierry Tillier / Benoit Piret
Tillier and Piret met in the early 80's, distant followers of the Fluxus movement and the mailart network, members of the Réseau 666, they collaborated for the creation of zines and xerox projects, etc... They exhibited together several times with their project "Les Colors du Sud", the first one at the Half a dozen roses gallery in Venice, California in 1997, then on second life and other mysterious different places...
